{
  "asrEngine": "Deepgram", 
  "recognitionEngineParameters": {
    "profanityFilter": false,
    "initialSilenceTimeoutMs": 8000,
    "endSilenceTimeoutMs": 1200,
    "speechContextPhrases": [],
    "sensitivity": 0.4,
    "model": "phonecall", 
    "language": "en-US",
    "punctuation": true,
    "diarize": false
  },
  "bargeInEnable": false,
  "bargeInThreshold": 0.6,
  "confidenceThreshold": 0.65,
  "noInputTimeout": 8000,
  "noMatchTimeout": 4000,
  "maxSpeechTimeout": 10000,
  "sessionParameters": {
    "enablePartialResults": true,
    "interimResultsTimeoutMs": 4000
  }
}

**Notes:**

| initialSilenceTimeoutMs: | 
|:-------------------------|
|Lets the prompt finish before assuming background noise is "speech." |

| endSilenceTimeoutMs: | 
|:---------------------|
| Wait for actual pause (not just split-second ambient noise). |

| sensitivity: |
|:-------------|
| Lowered to 0.4 so Deepgram ignores "low energy" background sounds. |

| bargeInEnable: |
|:---------------|
| false ensures full prompt plays before listening even starts. |

| model: |
|:-------|
| "phonecall" — this model is trained to expect noisy, low-fidelity environments. |

| punctuation: |
|:-------------|
| true — optional but makes transcripts easier to read. |
